                    "description": "Shifting Paradigms makes our tread on our planet lighter by supporting the transition to a low-carbon, circular economy. It applies a system\u2019s approach to both material and energy resources as a basis for sound business and policy development.\n\nBy mapping out the metabolism of a company or jurisdiction, Shifting Paradigms identifies opportunities to improve efficiency within a company, supply chain, city or region. It helps investors and industries benchmark their resource footprint, increase the use of sources that are regenerative, improve asset use and unite stakeholders behind a roadmap to a low-carbon and circular economy.\n\nAdvisor to UNDP, EBRD, ECF, NEFCO, GiZ, Worldbank, Almaty municipality, 17 municipalities in the Netherlands, Svilosa (Bulgaria), Nuetech Solar (India), Livebuild, SmartCrusher.nl.\nPartner organisations: Circle Economy, Fabrications, Climate Focus, Revolve Consulting (Armenia), BEROC (Belarus), Green Carbon (Bulgaria), Planet Ark (Australia) Center for Clean Production and Consumption (Kazakhstan), Whitehopleman Cement Consultants (UK).\n\nwww.shiftingparadigms.nl.",
